{
  "stem": "17626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 130.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kerchief with a little emblem, it was [NON-ENGLISH], you know, ready, always ready; you know, that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where I had, of course, made more friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And was-- it was OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was OK, other than the odd time I was called zhyd.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was this [NON-ENGLISH], you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a nice word for Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jew, Jew on a string, dancing on a string or running on a string.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was called a lot of times, yevreyka, which is another word for Jewess.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A politer form.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What made me different?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why did they call me yevreyka?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to school, I lived in the same-- I, I looked the same.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was-- there was no difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My, my Russian was perfect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know that I didn't know Russian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, I mean it was-- everything was just great, and I couldn't understand why I was called yevreyka.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was this underlying accepted, not accepted, as part of a group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was growing-- you know, I was five and six, and seven, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean this was very formative years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was something that you feel very intensely as a child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember one time being called-- everybody at Christmas, I mean Christmas was a big holiday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't celebrate Christmas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have a tree.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that made me different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the children say, you don't have a tree.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, I had to go and ask my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What is this Jewess?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And why don't we have a tree?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember one day being called in by a friend to their house to see the tree, and to partake of their, their meal.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
